## Prerequisites

- PHP 8.3+
- Composer 2.x
- Docker and Docker Compose

## Local Development

### Quick Start

```bash
make start
```

This starts the full stack (PHP-FPM, Nginx, PostgreSQL) via Docker Compose.

### Common Commands

```bash
make start       # Start all services
make stop        # Stop all services
make logs        # Follow all service logs
make bash        # Shell into the app container
make shell       # Open Tinker (Laravel REPL)
make test        # Run test suite
make migrate     # Run database migrations
make seed        # Run database seeders
make fresh       # Fresh migrate and seed
make install     # Install Composer dependencies
make lint        # Run code style fixer
make cache-clear # Clear all caches
```

### Manual Setup (without Docker)

```bash
composer install
cp .env.example .env
php artisan key:generate
php artisan migrate
php artisan serve
```

